                      'Rosetta func: '
                      'Create_OnDemandInterestPaymentPrimitiveInstruction — An '
                      'instruction to make a interium interest payment by adding a '
                      'payout leg to the deal.',
                      'Rosetta func: Create_TerminationInstruction — Creates the '
                      'relevant primitive instruction for a termination, which '
                      'consists in a quantity change to bring the quantity to zero.',
